{"tid":352762,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實馮天蔓真係一個好女仔","createTime":"2017-08-09T04:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T10:32:25.000Z","uid":134647,"like":14,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5c650221f7213854fbbef14d715d52f957a1e029","tid":352762,"uid":134647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:35:50.000Z","msg":"其實馮天蔓真係一個好女仔黎㗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個平凡之中又帶點不平凡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/122818_8c4bce0f476c4cee58dae804e3c83b71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F122818_8c4bce0f476c4cee58dae804e3c83b71.jpg&h=fea6251f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又好陽光<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/122838_ce03b54d641a3df032a2b04defce948f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F122838_ce03b54d641a3df032a2b04defce948f.jpg&h=e7fe30ab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/122850_bb903f07db73eb57a4a8f8a7efff668b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F122850_bb903f07db73eb57a4a8f8a7efff668b.jpg&h=6f350cf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n微微一笑真係成個心都融曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/122929_3859297d442772caeedd269d8c7b23bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F122929_3859297d442772caeedd269d8c7b23bc.jpg&h=a0229d52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n性格又好又可愛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/122957_0b0e3f18184aac99fe632ae0f074102d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F122957_0b0e3f18184aac99fe632ae0f074102d.jpg&h=e2d93132&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n把聲又甜 真係好adorable<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/123022_fe63ae44f2b6b3acc4fc5e58e2620bdc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F123022_fe63ae44f2b6b3acc4fc5e58e2620bdc.jpg&h=a265380c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有啊啲人成日話carry到all back先係女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/123248_ebfb70df3ebee101a851c233d8da4b96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F123248_ebfb70df3ebee101a851c233d8da4b96.jpg&h=7040ff33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n讀名女校而唔勾心鬥角真係好欣賞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">加油呀天蔓 好多人支持你der٩( ᐛ )و❤️</span>"},{"pid":"c5f5771bddc3b119722fabd820a24f19f79b19d9","tid":352762,"uid":1582,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:38:16.000Z","msg":"仲諗住最底有素顏圖<br />\n負評"},{"pid":"39589456d79a95cbbfa4d33140ec0a162950f8cb","tid":352762,"uid":134647,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:40:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲諗住最底有素顏圖<br />\n負評</blockquote><br />\n個張好明顯係Maybelline問題 佢中學好多相都素顏啦又唔見係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16277807139bf4966ca41e26d52af84bf5650314","tid":352762,"uid":1582,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T17:16:47.000Z","msg":"樓豬你有冇post snapchat 話第一次畀人負評 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" cla